    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<strong>If It’s for My Client, I’d Even Schedule a Demon Lord</strong> is a calendar-themed puzzle game where you set schedules while laughing at a parodical fantasy story. Prepare a schedule, one event at a time, to make your clients happy. Resolve schedule conflicts, explore unique worlds, and challenge this time management brain-teaser!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797560/extras/c832e4ef164c6f98b6b0608ddca9cc3a.avif?t=1750747789\" width=600 height=157 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>300+ puzzles!<br></li><li>Humorous adventure with unique characters.<br></li><li>See new schedules, calendars, and characters as you progress.<br></li><li>Explore common calendars with 365 days, and fantastical calendars with original days-of-the-week and months.<br></li><li>Deal with various types of events from one-time activities to weekly affairs!<br></li><li>Take your time, or race the clock.<br></li><li>Customize your own colour schemes, or enjoy the varying schemes level-by-level.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797560/extras/cf9b18e231e896d512d8619423860559.avif?t=1750747789\" width=184 height=184 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797560/extras/f80f6873ea5f649976ecb7d478a172b2.avif?t=1750747789\" width=184 height=184 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797560/extras/14a71d033fe5f8796e5fb384306d17e0.avif?t=1750747789\" width=184 height=184 /></span>",
